  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That we will be in Washington, to-- that will go so fast to get to Washington.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, he told me, I ask him, tell me, please, what's it that they are dividing Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember the history of the-- that this will be occupied, half of it till Vistula, he told me that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans will be on the other side to show that Poland was divided in half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the end was that the-- the demarcation line was on the River Bug, B-U-G.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back with them as they are.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he told me that the-- that the demarcation line-- line will be Vistula, Vistula is not far from Radom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was thinking to go closer to be [INAUDIBLE] and my father, to be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I find out that the demarcation line will be on the River Bug, I start to think I was without money to do something with my profession.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Kowel, I went to attempt back to Kowel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From Kowel I decided to go to Bialystok, because Bialystok is on the other side of the Bug, the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after I decided to go to Bialystok, because there are some tanneries there, that I will be able to establish myself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I noticed right away that this war that would definitely take a long, long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I know the history of Poland, and they have been not once divided between Germany, Austria, Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All by myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to one [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] gentleman, on the name Lazar Lewin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-A-Z-A-R, L-E-W-I-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a chemicalist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He got some representations of firms from overseas and he used to sell to my father some chemicals and extracts.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
